Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.760 --> 00:00:09.520
In this video, we will show you how to

00:00:09.520 --> 00:00:11.580
configure and use your Jabra headset

00:00:11.580 --> 00:00:14.660
with IBM Sametime.

00:00:14.660 --> 00:00:18.390
Call control with IBM Sametime is supported with installation

00:00:18.390 --> 00:00:21.640
of Jabra PC Suite on your PC.

00:00:21.640 --> 00:00:24.750
See the Jabra soft phone guide at Jabra.com for

00:00:24.750 --> 00:00:25.840
more details.

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:28.980
Open IBM Sametime.

00:00:28.980 --> 00:00:32.440
Click "File" then "Preferences".

00:00:34.640 --> 00:00:38.280
On the window that opens, click "Voice and Video".

00:00:43.940 --> 00:00:48.960
Under "Microphone", choose your Jabra headset.

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:53.940
Under speakers, choose your Jabra headset.

00:00:53.940 --> 00:00:58.680
Under ringing, choose your Jabra headset.

00:00:58.680 --> 00:01:03.680
When complete, click "Apply" then "OK".

00:01:03.680 --> 00:01:08.540
On an incoming call, your headset will ring to notify you.

00:01:08.540 --> 00:01:12.080
To answer the call from Sametime, click "Accept"

00:01:12.080 --> 00:01:13.380
on the call window.

00:01:14.380 --> 00:01:19.460
To answer the call from the headset, press the answer button.

00:01:19.460 --> 00:01:21.840
Increase listening volume by using the

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:24.900
headset volume control.

00:01:24.900 --> 00:01:27.860
Decrease listening volume by using the headset

00:01:27.860 --> 00:01:29.420
volume control.

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:36.560
To mute the call from Sametime, click the microphone icon on

00:01:36.680 --> 00:01:38.320
the call window.

00:01:39.380 --> 00:01:42.960
To mute the microphone from the headset, use the headset mute

00:01:42.960 --> 00:01:45.200
control.

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:49.320
To unmute the call from Sametime, click the microphone icon on the

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:51.680
call window.

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:55.560
To unmute the microphone from the headset, use the headset mute

00:01:55.560 --> 00:01:57.640
control.

00:02:01.340 --> 00:02:03.979
To end the call from Sametime, click the

00:02:03.980 --> 00:02:07.400
red handset on the call window.

00:02:07.400 --> 00:02:10.789
To end the call from the headset, use the end

00:02:10.789 --> 00:02:14.640
button.

00:02:14.640 --> 00:02:18.200
For more information, please visit Jabra.com/support.

00:02:18.200 --> 00:02:20.300
Thank you for watching.

